text: Fissistigma cupreonitens is a species of plant in the Annonaceae family. It is endemic to China. ==References== * China Plant Specialist Group 2004. Fissistigma cupreonitens. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 21 August 2007.
